Re: Spell Casting Mastery tests (no, NOT fury mastery)</span><hr size=1> Hmm, just to shoot down my own theory I summed up the tests sofar. <br>
<br>
The difference between the tests with full gear and C3 and the naked tests worry me. Maybe C3 doesnt have a mana component or the mana calc for high end levels is wrong. I guess I need to do a few full gear tests without C3 to check that part atleast.<br>
<br>
SCM0:<br>
200 skill: 2415 mana with 2185 mana = 9.5%<br>
200 skill: 2290 mana with 2044 mana = 10.7%<br>
200 skill: 2490 mana with 2174 mana = 12.7%<br>
50 skill: 2130 mana with 2044 mana = 4.0%<br>
<br>
SCM2:<br>
200 skill: 4975-5125 mana with 4440 mana = 12.0-13.4% (~16% if C3 doesnt give +mana pool)<br>
200 skill: 1840-1860 mana with 1557 mana = 15.4-16.3%<br>
50 skill: 4580-4720 mana with 4440 mana = 3.1-5.9% (~9% if C3 doesnt givge +mana pool)<br>
<br>
SCM3:<br>
200 skill: 5900 mana with 4979 mana = 15.6% (~20%)<br>
