Assuming your correct that SCM3 moves the normal 11% reduction to 21% thats an increase in spells cast per mana bar of 12.7%. Unlike the extra 7% from CF those require more time and generate more aggro though but the effect is substantially larger too. For non-spec spells the effect of going from 3% reduction to 13% reduction is a gain of 11.5%, so thats also very usefull.<br>
